# FLOW_GOVERNANCE.md: The Khulula Protocol (Visual Edition)

> "I am because we are. The system thrives because we trust, not because we control."

**Status:** Version 1.1 (Lagos Pilot)  
**Philosophy:** Ubuntu-Systems Engineering  
**Purpose:** Human-centered governance to maximize Calm (L), Spontaneity (S), and Resonance (I) in a Flow Node.

