## â…¦. Practical Recommendations

- Assign **Flow Facilitators** per Node (1 per 10â€“15 participants)  
- Maintain **weekly reflections** to track L, S, I metrics  
- Keep **transparent logs** for Circle decisions (non-coercive)  
- Encourage **peer mentorship** for knowledge diffusion  

